able solution.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1408, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999996274255, \"rank\": 3.7257326452018046e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those populations\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"a durable solution\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France is preparing to host the Olympic Games in Paris, a multi-sport event that will take place from July 26 to Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999998310327846, \"rank\": 1.6647502776746946e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1492, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999996274255, \"rank\": 3.7257326452018046e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"a multi-sport event\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"History Editorial Guidelines Social Media Policies Executive Team Domestic Offices International Offices Logos Communication RSS Subscription Requests Announcement Service Quality Management Privacy and Cookies Policy Information Policy Diary Business News Finance Terminal Anadolu Images Energy Terminal AA Academy Green Line Discrimination Line Fact Check Line IPhone